{
  "stem": "24171.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they did there in Krakow, they were taking blood from us in the barracks a few times, I don't know for what.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- and as I was there, and then when they start, the one day, the girls came to the window there and say, Regina, try to get out, because we're going to be separated.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they were afraid because we asked once if somebody is really sick or whatever, what do they do with the people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, they're getting back to Auschwitz in the-- in the right place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so I went out of there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in between, in Plaszow, oh, there was other things going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were going on shooting thing too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a ditch not far away, at that hill, where things-- I was working there, and by the lumber too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not always the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And once we were kind of carrying big, big, this-- this thick of lumber, and we were five girls in between, because they were kind of really heavy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is where we were five, and we picked up that piece of lumber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in the meantime, there was a guy with a dog, and sometimes he had a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was chasing up the hill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was so muddy that the shoes, sometimes the mud poured down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, not mine, because mine was really good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I really thank for my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they had the problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And by the time he got to that lumber place, ready to stack the lumber, there were just two of us, or sometimes in the middle, one, because if it was really, really a long one.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it came up the hill.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
